OL,4,G0440FAuction: Shakespeare Special
OL,5,     GMore than 400 years after his
OL,6,     Gdeath, an example of the
OL,7,     Gcelebrated playwright's completed
OL,8,     Gwork - The First Folio - is up
OL,9,     Gfor auction at Christie's in New
OL,10,     GYork and could fetch millions.
OL,11,G0505FAuction
OL,12,     GThe marble lions from the tomb of
OL,13,     GCharles V of France are being
OL,14,     Gsold at Christie's, while an
OL,15,     Gexquisite Johann Christian Neuber
OL,16,     Gsnuff box comes under the hammer
OL,17,     Gat Sotheby's.
OL,18,G0530FAuction
